{"title": "Nginx \u5b89\u88c5", "date": "2018-11-28 15:26:11", "categories": "\u670d\u52a1\u5668", "tags": "Nginx", "keywords": "Nginx \u5b89\u88c5,Nginx", "description": "", "file_name": "Nginx-\u5b89\u88c5", "short": " \n Nginx (engine x) \u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ad8\u6027\u80fd\u7684HTTP\u548c\u53cd\u5411\u4ee3\u7406\u670d\u52a1\uff0c\u4e5f\u662f\u4e00\u4e2aIMAP/POP3/SMTP\u670d\u52a1\u3002Nginx\u662f\u7531\u4f0a\u6208\u5c14\u00b7\u8d5b\u7d22\u8036\u592b\u4e3a\u4fc4\u7f57\u65af\u8bbf\u95ee\u91cf\u7b2c\u4e8c\u7684Rambler.ru\u7ad9\u70b9\uff08\u4fc4\u6587\uff1a\u0420\u0430\u043c\u0431\u043b\u0435\u0440\uff09\u5f00\u53d1\u7684\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e00\u4e2a\u516c\u5f00\u7248\u672c0.1.0\u53d1\u5e03\u4e8e2004\u5e7410\u67084\u65e5\u3002 \n \n ", "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>Nginx (engine x) \u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ad8\u6027\u80fd\u7684HTTP\u548c\u53cd\u5411\u4ee3\u7406\u670d\u52a1\uff0c\u4e5f\u662f\u4e00\u4e2aIMAP/POP3/SMTP\u670d\u52a1\u3002Nginx\u662f\u7531\u4f0a\u6208\u5c14\u00b7\u8d5b\u7d22\u8036\u592b\u4e3a\u4fc4\u7f57\u65af\u8bbf\u95ee\u91cf\u7b2c\u4e8c\u7684Rambler.ru\u7ad9\u70b9\uff08\u4fc4\u6587\uff1a\u0420\u0430\u043c\u0431\u043b\u0435\u0440\uff09\u5f00\u53d1\u7684\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e00\u4e2a\u516c\u5f00\u7248\u672c0.1.0\u53d1\u5e03\u4e8e2004\u5e7410\u67084\u65e5\u3002</p>\n</blockquote>\n<!-- more -->\n<h4 id=\"nginx\">Nginx\u5b89\u88c5</h4>\n<p>yum\u6e90\u4e2d\u7684nginx\u7248\u672c\u6bd4\u8f83\u65e7\uff0c\u5305\u5b89\u88c5\u53ef\u4ee5\u6307\u5b9a\u5b89\u88c5\u7248\u672c\uff0c\u5b89\u88c5\u76ee\u5f55\u5730\u5740\u4e3a /usr/local/</p>\n<h5 id=\"_1\">\u5305\u5b89\u88c5</h5>\n<p>\u5b89\u88c5nginx\u6240\u9700\u7684\u4f9d\u8d56\u5e93\uff08\u9700\u5728root\u8eab\u4efd\u4e0b\uff09</p>\n<h6 id=\"pcre\">pcre\u5e93</h6>\n<ol>\n<li>\u4e0b\u8f7d pcre\u5e93 \u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># wget ftp://ftp.csx.cam.ac.uk/pub/software/programming/pcre/pcre-8.36.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\u89e3\u538b\u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># tar -zxvf pcre-8.36.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\u7f16\u8bd1\u5b89\u88c5</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># cd pcre-8.36</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># ./configure</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># make &amp;&amp; make install</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h6 id=\"zlib\">zlib\u5e93</h6>\n<ol>\n<li>\u4e0b\u8f7d zlib\u5e93 \u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># wget http://zlib.net/zlib-1.2.8.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\u89e3\u538b\u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># tar -zxvf zlib-1.2.8.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\u7f16\u8bd1\u5b89\u88c5</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># cd zlib-1.2.8</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># ./configure</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># make &amp;&amp; make install</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h6 id=\"ssl\">ssl\u5e93</h6>\n<ol>\n<li>\u4e0b\u8f7d zlib\u5e93 \u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># wget http://www.openssl.org/source/openssl-1.0.1j.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\u89e3\u538b\u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># tar -zxvf openssl-1.0.1j.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\u7f16\u8bd1\u5b89\u88c5</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># cd openssl-1.0.1j</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># ./configure</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># make &amp;&amp; make install</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h6 id=\"nginx_1\">\u4f9d\u8d56\u5e93\u5b89\u88c5\u5b8c\u540e\u5c31\u5f00\u59cb\u5b89\u88c5nginx</h6>\n<ol>\n<li>\u4e0b\u8f7d zlib\u5e93 \u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># wget http://nginx.org/download/nginx-1.7.4.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\u89e3\u538b\u5b89\u88c5\u5305</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># tar -zxvf nginx-1.7.4.tar.gz</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\u7f16\u8bd1\u5b89\u88c5</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># cd nginx-1.7.4</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># ./configure</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># make &amp;&amp; make install</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h5 id=\"yum\">yum \u5b89\u88c5</h5>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># yum install pcre pcre-devel</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># yum install zlib zlib-devel</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># yum install openssl openssl--devel</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># yum install nginx</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"nginx_2\">Nginx \u914d\u7f6e</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\u9996\u5148\u67e5\u770bnginx\u7684\u5b89\u88c5\u5730\u5740\uff0c\u4e00\u822c\u9ed8\u8ba4\u5b89\u88c5\u5728 /etc/nginx/nginx.conf</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># nginx -t  // root\u8eab\u4efd\u4e0b</span>\n// \u8f93\u51fa\nnginx: the configuration file /etc/nginx/nginx.conf syntax is ok\nnginx: configuration file /etc/nginx/nginx.conf <span class=\"nb\">test</span> is successful\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\u4fee\u6539\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># vim /etc/nginx/nginx.conf</span>\n\n// \u4fee\u6539\u683c\u5f0f\u5982\u4e0b\nserver <span class=\"o\">{</span>\nlisten       <span class=\"m\">80</span> default_server<span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"c1\"># \u76d1\u542c\u7684\u7aef\u53e3</span>\nlisten       <span class=\"o\">[</span>::<span class=\"o\">]</span>:80 default_server<span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"c1\"># \u76d1\u542c\u7684\u7aef\u53e3</span>\nserver_name  lianghuii.com<span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"c1\"># \u57df\u540d</span>\nroot         /home/hexo<span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"c1\"># \u7f51\u7ad9\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\uff0c\u9700\u586b\u5199\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u76ee\u5f55\u5730\u5740\uff0c\u6682\u65f6\u6ca1\u6709\u7528\u9ed8\u8ba4\u7684</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Load configuration files for the default server block.</span>\ninclude /etc/nginx/default.d/*.conf<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\nlocation / <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\nerror_page <span class=\"m\">404</span> /404.html<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">location</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> /40x.html <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\nerror_page <span class=\"m\">500</span> <span class=\"m\">502</span> <span class=\"m\">503</span> <span class=\"m\">504</span> /50x.html<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">location</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> /50x.html <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\u4fee\u6539\u4fdd\u5b58\u540e\u542f\u52a8nginx\u670d\u52a1</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># systemctl start nginx.service</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>\u8bbf\u95ee\u81ea\u5df1\u670d\u52a1\u5668\u516c\u7f51ip -&gt; http://123.123.123.123:80\uff08\u9ed8\u8ba480\u7aef\u53e3\uff09\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u80fd\u8bbf\u95ee\u6210\u529f\u8bc1\u660enginx\u5f00\u542f\u6210\u529f\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u8bbf\u95ee\u5931\u8d25<br />\n- \u7f51\u9875403  \u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\u7684\u7f51\u7ad9\u6839\u76ee\u5f55\u4e0b\u4e3a\u7a7a<br />\n- \u7f51\u9875404  \u68c0\u67e5\u4e91\u670d\u52a1\u5668\u662f\u5426\u914d\u7f6e\u4e86 80 \u7aef\u53e3\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u68c0\u67e5\u9632\u706b\u5899\u662f\u5426\u5f00\u653e\u4e8680\u7aef\u53e3</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"nginx_3\">Nginx \u547d\u4ee4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>nginx\u670d\u52a1\u72b6\u6001</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># systemctl status nginx.service</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\u542f\u52a8nginx\u670d\u52a1</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># systemctl start nginx.service</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\u505c\u6b62nginx\u670d\u52a1</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># systemctl stop nginx.service</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\u91cd\u542fnginx\u670d\u52a1</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># systemctl reload nginx.service</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"ip\">\u7981\u6b62IP\u76f4\u63a5\u8bbf\u95ee\u7f51\u7ad9</h4>\n<p>\u7981\u6b62\u522b\u4eba\u76f4\u63a5\u901a\u8fc7IP\u8bbf\u95ee\u7f51\u7ad9\uff0c\u5728nginx\u7684server\u914d\u7f6e\u6587\u4ef6\u524d\u9762\u52a0\u4e0a\u5982\u4e0b\u7684\u914d\u7f6e\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u6709\u901a\u8fc7IP\u76f4\u63a5\u8bbf\u95ee\u7684\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u62d2\u7edd\u8fde\u63a5\u3002\u5728\u914d\u7f6e\u524d\u9762\u52a0\u4e00\u4e2aserver\uff0c\u5982\u4e0b</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>server <span class=\"o\">{</span>\nlisten   <span class=\"m\">80</span> default_server<span class=\"p\">;</span>\nlisten   <span class=\"o\">[</span>::<span class=\"o\">]</span>:80 default_server<span class=\"p\">;</span>\nserver_name  _<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"m\">444</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>\u6dfb\u52a0\u540e\uff1a</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>server <span class=\"o\">{</span>\nlisten   <span class=\"m\">80</span> default_server<span class=\"p\">;</span>\nlisten   <span class=\"o\">[</span>::<span class=\"o\">]</span>:80 default_server<span class=\"p\">;</span>\nserver_name  _<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"m\">444</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\nserver <span class=\"o\">{</span>\nlisten       <span class=\"m\">80</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\nserver_name  lianghuii.com<span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"c1\"># \u57df\u540d</span>\nroot         /home/hexo<span class=\"p\">;</span> <span class=\"c1\"># \u7f51\u7ad9\u6839\u76ee\u5f55</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Load configuration files for the default server block.</span>\ninclude /etc/nginx/default.d/*.conf<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\nlocation / <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\nerror_page <span class=\"m\">404</span> /404.html<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">location</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> /40x.html <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\nerror_page <span class=\"m\">500</span> <span class=\"m\">502</span> <span class=\"m\">503</span> <span class=\"m\">504</span> /50x.html<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">location</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> /50x.html <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}